<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10346</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17682</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾格尼丝看着艾伦一天天长大，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17682</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>作为女巫，她为自己的咒语感到骄傲。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“国王和王后每天都在担心艾伦，”她高兴地想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30150</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39957</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们的女儿将永远那么轻、那么傻！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，艾格尼丝路过湖边，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46747</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看到了在湖里游泳的艾伦！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46747</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她像小鱼那样自由地游来游去，笑得非常开心 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哼！”艾格尼丝的眼睛闪着蓝色的光，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我应该想到水的！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>水里是公主唯一能得到自由的地方！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68399</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>回到家，女巫生气地走来走去：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要一个新的咒语，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个更厉害的咒语！”她想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“艾伦将失去她最爱的湖，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而王国将失去所有的水！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾格尼丝急忙走到一个箱子前，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她取出了一些干海草，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后把海草放进一桶漂满药粉的水里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她一边念着咒语一边搅拌药水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114031</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，一个动物从水里钻了出来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>发出嘶嘶的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是一条闪闪发光的水龙！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125678</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125678</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女巫把水龙放在她的肩膀上，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我要拿上所有地下室的钥匙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾格尼丝抓起一个巨大的钥匙环，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>上面有100把钥匙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后她走到一个地下室的门前，打开了门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她下了几个台阶，来到另一个门前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151210</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157209</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她打开门，然后又下了几个台阶，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157209</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>来到另一个门前……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就这样，一直到100个门全部打开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>走下最后的台阶，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172746</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这里是一个巨大的洞穴！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172746</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一根根石柱支撑着顶部。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女巫抬头看向洞顶，嘎嘎笑了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洞顶的上面就是湖底！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾格尼丝举起水龙，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194443</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>水龙抬起头，不停地在洞顶寻找着什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204147</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，水龙的头向一块石头伸去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204147</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207746</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你找到它了！”女巫说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207746</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212421</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“去把湖水吸干，我的宝贝！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212421</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>水龙紧紧地吸在那块石头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾格尼斯松开手，让水龙吊在空中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223073</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后她坐了下来，开始织毛衣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231211</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的黑猫走过来躺在她的脚边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231211</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241889</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“安静点儿！我们要在这里等水龙施完法。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>